Package oracle.kubernetes.operator.rest.resource

Class ClustersResource

java.lang.Object
oracle.kubernetes.operator.rest.resource.BaseResource
oracle.kubernetes.operator.rest.resource.ClustersResource
public class ClustersResource
extends BaseResource
ClustersResource is a jaxrs resource that implements the REST api for the /operator/{version}/domains/{domainUID}/clusters path. It can be used to list a WebLogic domain's clusters.
